                     CHAOSCASTLE - DISTRIBUTION
                     ==========================

ChaosCastle is SHAREWARE. As is, only about 30% of all levels are avaiable.
If you like this game and want to play all levels, I encourage you to
register by sending US$ 15 (or 20 Swiss Francs) to the author. In return,
you will receive a personal keyfile with a password that enable all
features.
